'''天主教阿本古魯教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Abenguruensis}}；{{lang-fr|Diocèse de Abengourou}}）是[[科特迪瓦|科特迪瓦]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教布瓦凱總教區|布瓦凱總教區]]。

教區成立於1963年9月13日，<ref>{{cite web |title=ABIDJANENSIS ET ALIARUM (ABENGURUENSIS) |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19630913_abidjanensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-09-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930095621/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19630913_abidjanensis.html |archivedate=2019-09-30 |language=la |date=1963-09-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>位於[[中科莫埃區|中科莫埃區]]，2004年有教友295,000人（佔轄區總人口49.1%）、二十個堂區、四十九名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-de|格巴亞·博義·齊里|Gbaya Boniface Ziri}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 01.07.2009 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/07/01/0445/01047.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-09-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930094510/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/07/01/0445/01047.html |archivedate=2019-09-30 |language=it |date=2009-07-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|勃路諾·夸梅|Bruno Kouamé}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 21.11.2003 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2003/11/21/0588/01820.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-09-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929144122/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2003/11/21/0588/01820.html |archivedate=2019-09-29 |language=it |date=2003-11-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

